  <brief_title>Use of a Radiopaque Localizer Grid and Methylene Blue Staining as an Aid to Reduce Radiation Exposure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of a Radiopaque Localizer Grid and Methylene Blue Staining as an Aid to Reduce Radiation Exposure in Resection Small Femur Lesions</official_title>
  <sponsors>
